title: Bobby Starts The Show Upset + Amy Got To Visit Her Dad + Luke Bryan Doing American Idol From The House

description:
Bobby starts the show a little upset over all the negativity that came after having Dr. Fauci on as a guest. Amy got to visit her dad at his place by talking through the glass door! Plus, Luke Bryan calls the show to talk about doing American Idol from his house!
